## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>не следует вызывать до завершения загрузки документа, реализующего его.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-161">После обработки <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> события можно определить, завершена загрузка документа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-161">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-162">В следующем примере показано, как вызвать функцию скрипта в документе из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] приложения с помощью. <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-162">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-163">В этом примере функция скрипта не имеет параметров.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-163">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-164">Ниже [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] приведен документ, реализующий функцию сценария, которая будет вызываться из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-164">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-165">Ниже показана [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] реализация для вызова функции скрипта [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] в документе.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-165">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>не следует вызывать до завершения загрузки документа, реализующего его.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-174">После обработки <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> события можно определить, завершена загрузка документа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-174">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-175">Если не передать достаточное количество значений параметров в скрипт, который вызывается, то параметры, в которые не передаются значения, будут иметь неопределенное значение.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-175">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-176">Если передается слишком много значений параметров, лишние значения игнорируются.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-176">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-177">В следующем примере показано, как вызывать функции скрипта в документе из приложения с помощью <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-177">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-178">В этом примере для функций скрипта требуются параметры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-178">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-179">Ниже приведен документ, который реализует функции скрипта, которые будут вызываться из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-179">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-180">Ниже показана [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] реализация для вызова функций скрипта [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] в документе.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-180">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-194">Вызов <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> оказывает тот же результат, что и <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> установка свойства.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-194">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>используется из разметки разработчиками, которые хотят декларативно указывать исходный документ, который <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> переходит к, когда <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> инициализируется.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-196"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> Используйте метод, чтобы перейти по URL-адресу, который может содержать символы escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-197">Используйте метод для перехода к объекту, <xref:System.Uri> который не содержит escape-символы. <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-197">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f08f7-198">В следующем примере показано, как использовать <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> для перехода к документу с <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> помощью метода.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f08f7-198">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
